message.content:
Breakfast:
- Scrambled tofu with spinach and tomatoes
- Fresh fruit salad (strawberries, blueberries, pineapple)
- Green smoothie (kale, banana, mango, coconut water)

Lunch:
- Quinoa salad with chickpeas, cucumber, bell peppers, olives, and lemon dressing
- Steamed broccoli with a drizzle of olive oil and salt
- Fresh mixed greens salad (arugula, spinach, romaine) topped with cherry tomatoes, red onion, and avocado slices. Dressing: balsamic vinegar and extra virgin olive oil.

Dinner:
- Grilled chicken breast seasoned with salt, pepper, and herbs de Provence
- Roasted sweet potatoes (seasoned with cinnamon and nutmeg)
- Steamed asparagus topped with lemon juice and freshly ground black pepper

Snacks:
- Fresh fruit (apple or pear)
- Handful of sunflower seeds or pumpkin seeds
